---
---

<section class="relative py-20 md:py-28 overflow-hidden" style="background-color: var(--clr-primary);">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 noise-bg"></div>

  <!-- Decorative cream / blue blurs -->
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-25" style="background-color: var(--clr-cream);"></div>
  <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-64 h-64 rounded-full blur-3xl opacity-20" style="background-color: var(--clr-blue);"></div>

  <!-- Huge faded "14" -->
  <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-20 pointer-events-none select-none opacity-[0.08]">
    <span class="text-[20rem] leading-none font-bold text-cream" style="font-family: var(--font-heading); font-style: italic;">14</span>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-5 text-center relative z-10">
    <span class="chip-limited mb-6" style="background-color: var(--clr-cream);">
      Quedan pocos cupos este mes
    </span>

    <h3 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-6xl font-medium mb-5 md:mb-6 tracking-tight leading-[1.05] mt-6" style="font-family: var(--font-heading); color: var(--clr-cream);">
      Trabajamos con <span class="italic-accent">solo cinco</span>
      <br class="hidden sm:block"/>marcas al mes.
    </h3>

    <p class="text-cream/70 mb-10 text-base md:text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Si te interesa cuidar tu presencia digital con una agencia que elige a quién atender, conversemos.
    </p>

    <a href="#contacto" class="btn-cream text-base md:text-lg !py-4 md:!py-5 !px-10 md:!px-12">
      Quiero mi cupo &rarr;
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
